Class TagAccess.Sequence.Operation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.zebra.rfid.api3.TagAccess.Sequence.Operation
  • Enclosing class:
    TagAccess.Sequence
    public class TagAccess.Sequence.Operation
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a single operation that is to be added to the Tag Access Operation Sequence.
